        public static Collection<Statement> getStatements(Perspective p,
                                                  User user)
        Converts the Perspective, its Insights and Parameters (and ordering!) to Statements for adding to a Repository. If any Perspective, Insight, or Parameter is missing an ID, a new one will be generated for it, and set on the object
        Parameters:
        p - the perspective to convert.
        Returns:
        a list of statements that completely represent the perspective tree
